Content:: Walter Goldbeck (12 February 1945 – 2 July 2022) was a German politician. A member of the Free Democratic Party, he served in the Landtag of Mecklenburg-Vorpommern from 1990 to 1994.[1] Goldbeck died in July 2022 at the age of 77.[2]  This biography article about a member of the German Free Democratic Party (FDP) is a stub.
